name: Stereo Madness
author: RobTop
description: Stereo Madness is the first level in Geometry Dash. It is a very simple level that introduces the player to the basic mechanics of the game, such as jumping, flying, and avoiding obstacles. The level is set in a colorful and vibrant world, with a catchy soundtrack that adds to the overall experience. The level is designed to be easy for beginners, but still provides a challenge for more experienced players.
